Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰头地点是维尼特团子店前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 你到底打算睡到几时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}王宫内 机关宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜尔可队长似乎从昨天起就没回过房间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私自外宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 队长一定不会做那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定队长她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或许和莱纳·琉特在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}歼灭眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行的 请您站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能佩剑进去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉 我努力阻拦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 她是我的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？陛下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 艾丝莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 你退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想当我的护卫去艾斯塔布尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们俩计划逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 莱纳却没出现在约定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是也想逃离和你的团子之旅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有没有什么奇怪的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 昨天他好像见过我兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过露西尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里之前 我回了趟宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为莱纳说不定会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为何要去见露西尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长也不肯告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和莱纳之间发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳…消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帮我背团子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真的 大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩大人快介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有事要报告陛下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布尔的克拉乌前辈发来了报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉乌发来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布尔出现了复写眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎造成了相当大的损害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉乌率领罗兰德军和艾斯塔布尔军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往讨伐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…是莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳失踪是在今晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是复写眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉乌前辈也没那么容易对付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要前往艾斯塔布尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援克拉乌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名复写眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必须秘密保护起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是详细了解复写眼的难得机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝 搜索莱纳的事交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以自由使唤这两人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}旧艾斯塔布尔领内 森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是复写眼持有者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝无差错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常进入我的领地 袭击领民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑发 黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑瞳中闪耀的红色纹样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这复写眼的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诓骗我们公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取我们国家的罗兰德帝国元帅之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我好好见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑发 黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑瞳中闪耀的红色纹样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看起来真是美味无比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克帝国首都 格连斯雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样小小一个村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是连北方大陆最强大的史特欧尔公国
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是其手下败将的国家的首都？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有吃人妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大肆破坏的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者末裔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里满是神话传说的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是个奇怪的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏如此 我终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界上有些人拥有人称“魔眼”的特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人视能力不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼中有不同的纹样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以窥视别人梦境的“梦置眼”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吞噬人命的“歼灭眼”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说能解读所有魔法的“复写眼”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外还有“未来眼”“怨嗟眼”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前已确认的就是这五种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼持有者出生时和人类的小孩没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说其双眼只需一扫就能识破世界的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解读空气中扩散的结构
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间理解魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 还会因某种契机而发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理崩溃 企图抹消所有结构
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼持有者一旦发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法再恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说莱纳不是复写眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩溃的黑之勇者 害怕寂寞的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 真是热爱学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷法尔·埃迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如休息一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿有香醇的茶水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这国王在这里有什么好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐·诺尔兹二等兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:10:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的女人的名字 当然会想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你调查过我的事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光查名字有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是追你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部下说想查你的生平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我让他们别查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追女孩的时候不正面突破就没意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我为什么要来你这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是别国的间谍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自信还是有点看女人的眼光的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且同为痛恨战争的白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们合得来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上哪有人会喜欢战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也痛恨战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这个国家有你想知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始光是利用一下也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用我 利用这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.32,0:11:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这期间我一定会让你爱上我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给我喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}旧艾斯塔布尔领内 贝尔特村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 请看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:11:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了 终于
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个人的身体都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排好阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大规模魔法 准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那家伙 给我干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 用餐完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去找人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人类来说真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神十足的肉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 成长得好美味的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天你没杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元帅阁下 能打赢复写眼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然以人类来说 很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文 将舞于天空的光之魔兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为同伴报仇 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死的 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其释放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元帅阁下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红指克拉乌…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 镇定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 您没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时没下手真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 力量喷涌而出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下 这下我难保不将这里的所有人杀个精光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要勉强了 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是暂时撤退 先行治疗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这伤势反正逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来挡住那怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁此机会你带军队撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听的话你也没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我给席恩和诺娅带个好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要帮你跟公主殿下传话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你…快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睁开眼看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让克拉乌元帅阁下安全撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙…一群蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们罗兰德的人都是蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是蠢得无药可救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 只好帮你们一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮他们罗兰德的蠢货一把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大规模魔法发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会把同伴都卷进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙应该会吸收魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样能拖延时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜尔可队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克前辈 做了很美味的蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快出来吧 蜜尔可队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特今晨离开了旅店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蜜尔可队长到访之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封命令书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许给他看是个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们藏在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你们找我究竟有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜尔可·卡拉德人在我们手上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我们走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克·斯塔卡德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我拒绝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜尔可·卡拉德就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得莱纳·琉特把队长带走不大对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虏走队长的是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而目标是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰里吧嗦什么呢 还不乖乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这是魔法陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请别乱动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要动一下脚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会消失得连根指头也不剩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想让同为罗兰德服务的人们丧命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们的动作就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是在罗兰德受过武术训练的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而说到拥有像你这样的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会绑架蜜尔可·卡拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又找我有事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米兰·弗洛瓦德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事早调查清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德大人 实在抱…歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是米兰·弗洛瓦德中将吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 卢克·斯塔卡德中士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的强大我很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二场战役无败绩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全都是在难以形容的劣势情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你查得很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本所有战役中我都没用真名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的对手 似乎连小试牛刀也算不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜尔可队长在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事想请你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如陛下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你杀掉莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影 现形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:20:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你再动一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指和脑袋都会分家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好帮她背团子的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时冲动跑出来了可是手头基本没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥会有货币经济这玩意儿存在啊麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 好想去个只需要睡觉的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}被诅咒的瞳眸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是相当迫切的希望
